v2_542bb975.description: Auto-generated translation for: FluentAI turns your everyday entertainment into effective language lessons. v2_548d3e48.description: Auto-generated translation for: FluentAI is a browser extension that helps you learn languages while watching videos. v2_092c62d4.message: FluentAI mendukung semua bahasa melalui sistem penerjemahan yang didukung oleh AI kami.
